<li>Matthew Hilton, "Consumers and the State Since the Second World War." The ANNALS of the American Academy of Political and Social Science 611, no. 66 (2007): 66-81.</li>
<li>Heather Murray, "Free for All Lesbians: Lesbian Cultural Production and Consumption in the United States during the 1970s." <i>Journal of the History of Sexuality</i> 16, no. 2 (2007): 251-68.</li>
<li>H. Tschachtler, "Despotic Reason in Arcadia. Ernest Callenbach's Ecological Utopias", <i>Science-Fiction Studies</i> 11 (1984), pp. 304-317.</li>
<li>Scott Timberg,, New York Times article 12/14/2008 <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/14/fashion/14ecotopia.html" class="external text" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/14/fashion/14ecotopia.html" rel="nofollow">The Novel That Predicted Portland</a></li>
</ul>
